From Marc Thibault Subject Re Once tapped your code is no good any In article Jerry Han writes GUESS WHAT PEOPLE You live in one of the few countries in the world where a person can complain without getting shot Only guessing but from his address I'd say that Jerry like me lives in Unlike me he thinks that our friends in the US enjoy the same freedom that we do and he has not seen the slow but steady erosion to the south of We have the benefit of relatively slow politicians and ineffective law Our rednecks tend to be the objects of derision rather than elected It's everything LE can do to keep up with the real Any time they actually go after somebody just because they don't like his or her attitude it's national news It also often blows up in their faces the well intentioned but flawed Zundel case which resulted in a scolding from the Supreme Court not only to LE for prosecuting the case but to Parliament for passing the law it was prosecuted under Our friends south of the border don't have as easy a time of Among other things they have as many LE agencies as we have agencies and some of them have They also have the War on Drugs which gives law enforcement agencies exceptional powers to ignore individuals' rights the DEA has more arbitrary power than that given to Canadian agencies under the War Measures Act We have the RCMP and CSIS who can't stop fighting each other long enough to do any really effective suppression of private citizens' Not only that our Police Commissions have teeth as I learned when I had to fend off a bent It may be ironic that the nation founded on Life Liberty and the Pursuit of Happiness is getting government imposed order while the nation founded on Peace Order and Good Government is getting in your face That's not to say our time won't It looks like Chretien is going to run on a law and order Be Cheers Marc Marc Thibault Automation Architect CIS Oxford Mills Ontario Canada NC FreeNet BEGIN PGP PUBLIC KEY BLOCK hihtneFrrn vuEcSavh HLnv END 